{"tid":1475130,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"［8月15日］港元拆息全線抽升 1個月升穿2.1厘","createTime":"2019-08-15T11:20:04.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-15T18:49:11.000Z","uid":54733,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"96818672577511e4382dbd3a5f5ef20ef5d75c24","tid":1475130,"uid":54733,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T11:20:04.000Z","msg":"【信報財經新聞】港元拆息(HIBOR)全線走高，其中與樓按相關的1個月HIBOR連升3日，並升穿2.1厘水平，報2.14286厘，較周三高0.31215厘。<br />\n<br />\n據財資市場公會網頁顯示，港元隔夜拆息報1.2厘，較周三彈0.78643厘；1星期拆息回升至1.71857厘；兩星期拆息上揚至1.88228厘；3個月拆息走高至2.35厘。<br />\n<br />\n長息方面，半年期拆息上升至2.36054厘；1年期拆息上揚至2.4325厘。<br />\n<br />\n港滙方面，截至上午11時20分，港元兌美元報7.8387。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://finance.now.com/mobile/news/article/527450\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffinance.now.com%2Fmobile%2Fnews%2Farticle%2F527450&d=LSsgDEuqvL%2F6lC7PehFbg3lPKE5%2BvOhv5kPCmhOEeDs%3D&h=deec00ed\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://finance.now.com/mobile/news/article/527450</a>"},{"pid":"5493aaecc13dd63e897da6f333a03f8bc4644777","tid":1475130,"uid":296952,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T11:20:39.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">NOW OR NEVER</span></span></strong>"},{"pid":"160c7a009f653d76313cf3ef3f5c43a5497cee6d","tid":1475130,"uid":296952,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5493aaecc13dd63e897da6f333a03f8bc4644777","tid":1475130,"uid":296952,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T11:20:39.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">NOW OR NEVER</span></span></strong>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T11:20:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/kADi49W.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FkADi49W.jpg&h=52d5c214&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/9T512WB.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2